  "body": "@ibrkhalil I have updated the issue and added couple more cases when screen orientation change gets enabled on Android. \r\n\r\nAndroid only. Tested on Samsung Galaxy A52, Android 12\r\n\r\n**Case 1:** Orientation change is enabled on Sign in by syncing onboarding \r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Open Sign in by syncing onboarding screen\r\n2. Try to scan invalid QR code \r\n3. Try to change screen mode to landscape at the moment when error \"Oops! This is not a sync QR code\" appears \r\n4. See if it is possible to switch to landscape mode\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** can switch to landscape mode. \r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/230921887-91bc2881-e195-4617-adb8-6aed7dfe3d25.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n**Case 2:** Orientation change is enabled when Request to join community/New chat bottom sheets are opened\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/235913260-3fb26ade-9661-4f8e-842d-b4812b81d198.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/235913267-9016cd83-4317-44c3-8b9f-eb3334bcf1cf.mp4\r\n\r\n**Case 3:** Orientation change is enabled when notification toast appears\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/235913497-6fddd5d2-f2a8-4fb3-800a-a5645963d8a2.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
